    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Chop your<strong> tomato[es] </strong>roughly</p><p>Deseed your <strong>sweet pointed pepper[s] </strong>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop roughly</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
