            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>couscous</strong> to a heatproof bowl with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>dried oregano </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and 200ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [300ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Stir together, then cover and set aside – this is your <strong>herby couscous</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-3-1718102498673-x200.jpg",
