            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pepper is starting to soften, add the<strong> chopped garlic</strong> to the pan with your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>dried</strong> <strong>oregano</strong> and <strong>capers</strong></p><p>Cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
