          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> to the pan with 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml] <span class=\"text-danger\">[</span>250ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> and stir it all together</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
